short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GitHub interface supporter for lazy developers

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Written to make the GitHub homepage more customizable, this plugin is fully native and privacy-conscious, making your work your only focus and allowing you to create your own home environment. 

Also this extension able to redirect some group of websites like Spotify via clicking some text or icon.
